@startuml
actor "运维人员" as Operator
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "Spring Boot后端" as Backend
participant "采集适配器" as Collector
database "Prometheus" as Prometheus
participant "node_exporter" as Exporter
database "MySQL" as DB

Operator -> Frontend : 打开监控大屏
Frontend -> Backend : GET /api/dashboard/latest-metrics
Backend -> Collector : queryMetrics(deviceId)
Collector -> Prometheus : /api/v1/query?query=PromQL
Prometheus -> Exporter : scrape metrics
Exporter --> Prometheus : CPU/内存/磁盘/网络指标
Prometheus --> Collector : 指标查询结果
Collector -> Collector : 统一指标格式转换
Collector --> Backend : 返回设备指标
Backend -> DB : 保存最新指标
Backend --> Frontend : 返回大屏数据
Frontend --> Operator : 展示真实采集指标
@enduml
